riot now has 1 million plus job openings lol

Just as an aside -- lots of Rioters don't have "Riot" on our names (like me, for example). So just because you haven't seen the tag in a game doesn't mean you haven't had a Rioter on your team (or on the other team).

Folks around here play lots of League and sit in a wide spectrum of skill levels; it's probably more common than you might imagine to have a Riot person pop in your games. Course, the only thing that really matters is that everyone is being excellent to each other.

